{"tid":631201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭展出「自殺膠囊」　醫生發明家倡安樂死","createTime":"2018-04-16T09:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T21:13:35.000Z","uid":53379,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a6aceb36bf26ffcab7c0386fcbee8e79c8695b","tid":631201,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荷蘭展出「自殺膠囊」　醫生發明家倡安樂死<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180415/s00005/cd97cb7092f51e70a5a74469eecc0843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180415%2Fs00005%2Fcd97cb7092f51e70a5a74469eecc0843.jpg&h=e986c6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭一個葬禮展覽會展出一個「自殺膠囊」，用家只要按下按鈕，膠囊會注入氮氣，在內的人便會死亡。有份發明這機器的醫生認為，人有權利選擇何時死亡，多年來一直倡議安樂死。<br />\n<br />\n「自殺膠囊」名為「Sarco」，是石棺英文「sarcophagus」的縮寫，由澳洲醫生尼奇克（Philip Nitschke）及荷蘭設計師班尼克（Alexander Bannink）發明。用家使用機器前，必須先完成一份心理問卷，確保心智正常。之後用家會獲發一組4位密碼，輸入密碼才可進入膠囊。在膠囊內，用家還需先進行聲音辨識等程序，才能啟動機器。當用家按下按鈕，膠囊便會注入氮氣，他隨後或會感到暈眩，然後很快便失去意識並且死亡。<br />\n<br />\n「自殺膠囊」的模型現時在阿姆斯特丹舉行的葬禮展覽會展出，模型配備虛擬實境（VR）眼鏡，讓參觀者體驗卧在膠囊中，按下「死亡按鈕」前的感受。尼奇克打算在年底前，製造真正能夠使用的「自殺膠囊」，並把設計檔案上傳至互聯網，讓人下載並用3D列印製作膠囊。<br />\n<br />\n尼奇克多年來一直推動安樂死，對於安樂死的爭議，他指在很多國家，自殺並不違法，只是幫助他人自殺才是犯法。他又認為選擇何時死亡是基本人權，覺得若一個人獲得「生命」這份珍貴的禮物，也應能選擇適時送出禮物。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社／每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180415/s00005/1523770567293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180415%2Fs00005%2F1523770567293&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BFwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4dded879\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180415%2Fs00005%2F1523770567293&h=29187877\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180415/s00005/1523770567293</a><br />\n<br />\n唉 點解唔比安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2308056d857015c0b572589f9735aeb5cbd7ffd5","tid":631201,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"吸氮氣死會唔會辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f28bcd8d9a4940e2a8ec520bdb3c675a82e9bb","tid":631201,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"香港需要引入呢樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6215b777dc0c742e84d8c235f10c7532342364d6","tid":631201,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"Where is Monday"},{"pid":"d1dd8e82dca9f62a8f0821722f4a1cf9af74b3dd","tid":631201,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2308056d857015c0b572589f9735aeb5cbd7ffd5","tid":631201,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"吸氮氣死會唔會辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"唔會 會暈<br />\n暈左就咩都feel唔到<br />\n再慢慢缺氧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20a552ab781a5868bec3db4785cd642e821346b","tid":631201,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"我想死果陣有個人攬住我, 摸住我隻手或者頭"},{"pid":"d1808e8e6ad7cbd0b1225b6ad5bfdfe67e1fb96d","tid":631201,"uid":120965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1dd8e82dca9f62a8f0821722f4a1cf9af74b3dd","tid":631201,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2308056d857015c0b572589f9735aeb5cbd7ffd5","tid":631201,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"吸氮氣死會唔會辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"唔會 會暈<br />\n暈左就咩都feel唔到<br />\n再慢慢缺氧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.